quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  8,65,Aey nabi! Eman walon ko jihad ka shoq dilao agar tum mein bees (20) bhi sabar kerney walay hongay to do so per ghalib rahey gay. Aur agar tum mein aik so hongay to aik hazar kafiron per ghalib rahen gay iss wastay kay woh bey samajh log hain
  8,66,Acha abb Allah tumhara bojh halka kerta hai woh khoob janta hai kay tum mein na tawani hai pus agar tum mein say aik so sabar kerney walay hongay to woh do so per ghalib rahen gay aur agar tum mein aik hazar hongay to woh Allah kay hukum say do hazar per ghalib rahen gay Allah sabar kerney walon kay sath hai
  8,67,Nabi kay haath mein qaidi nahi chahaiye jabtak kay mulk mein achi khoonrezi ki jang na hojaye. Tum to duniya kay maal chahatay ho aur Allah ka irada aakhirat ka hai aur Allah zor aawar ba hikmat hai
  8,68,Agar pehlay hi say Allah ki taraf say baat likhi hui na hoti to jo kuch tum ney liya hai iss baray mein tumhen koi bari saza hoti
  8,69,Pus jo kuch halal aur pakeezah ghanimat tum ney hasil ki hai khoob khao piyo aur Allah say dartay raho yaqeenan Allah ghafoor-o-rahim hai